http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Visakhapatnam/Close-call-for-Kakinada-MP/article14005126.ece

Kakinada MP Thota Narasimham escaped with very simple bruises, as the car in which he was travelling met with an accident, near Nakkapalli tollgate, here on Sunday.The MP was travelling in an SVU from Kakinada to Visakhapatnam, when the car hit a road divider at around 7.15 p.m.Road dividerAccording to Yellamanchili Circle Inspector Venkat Rao, the car would have hit the road divider, as the median was at a low level in that area and due to insufficient lighting and fog.Simple bruisesThe MP sustained very simple bruises, but car was damaged.He shifted into another car and proceeded to Visakhapatnam, within a few minutes after the accident, said Mr. Venkat Rao.